704444f-b.title: Brooklyn: Franklin Avenue - Dean Street
704444f-b.text:
Franklin Avenue, at Dean Street. View 1 is south along the west side of Franklin Avenue, view 2 showing the corner end part of
Dean Street.
View 3 is north on Nranklin Avenue from Dean, showing the west
side.
P. L. Sperr  September 6, 1941
NO REPRODDCTEONR  Views 1-3
704444f-b.folder: Franklin Avenue & Dean Street, Brooklyn, NY
